      "y": 180,
      "width": 60,
      "height": 400,
      "text": "自身峰值比\n(本月熟手人均 ÷ 近6月峰值)\n\n>85% 正常发挥\n65-85% 有下滑空间\n<65% 严重未发挥",
      "fontSize": 13,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "fill": "#1e3a5f"
